urls.title: Ex-MI6 boss says coronavirus likely engineered in Wuhan lab
urls.description: A former head of the British intelligence agency MI6 was quoted in The Telegraph's Planet Normal podcast that he believes the COVID-19 outbreak was engineered in a lab and spread through coincidence.
